WHICH IS WHY SHE WAS
STAYING AT THE CEDRIC.

00:00:15.315 --> 00:00:16.916 align:start size:66% position:34%
SHE COULD PAY IN CASH
AND REMAIN ANONYMOUS

00:00:16.949 --> 00:00:18.651 size:59% position:70%
