OR SO DANGEROUS,

00:00:21.421 --> 00:00:22.789
SHE HAD TO MAKE SURE THEY
COULDN'T TRACE IT BACK TO HER.

00:00:22.822 --> 00:00:24.523 align:start position:0%
AND EVEN IF THEY DID
TRACE IT BACK TO HER,

00:00:24.557 --> 00:00:26.626
THEY'D STILL HAVE TO FIND HER
AMONGST HUNDREDS OF RESIDENTS.

00:00:26.659 --> 00:00:28.728 size:75% position:63%
SO SHE CREATED
A WHOLE FALSE PERSONA.

00:00:28.762 --> 00:00:30.229 size:88% position:56%
AND WHO'S GONNA LOOK TWICE
AT A RUNAWAY HOOKER?

00:00:30.263 --> 00:00:31.998 size:84% position:58%
I MEAN, SHE'S LIKE THE GIRL
WITH THE DRAGON TATTOO.

00:00:32.031 --> 00:00:33.299 align:start position:0%
ONLY THEY DID FIND HER,

00:00:33.332 --> 00:00:34.867 size:81% position:41%
WHICH IS WHY WE CAN'T FIND
HER LAPTOP.

00:00:34.901 --> 00:00:36.336 size:84% position:42%
WHOEVER SHE WENT UP AGAINST

00:00:36.369 --> 00:00:38.037 align:start position:0%
KILLED HER AND TOOK IT.

00:00:38.070 --> 00:00:39.806
UH, PROBLEM. WE DON'T KNOW
WHO SHE WENT UP AGAINST,

00:00:39.839 --> 00:00:41.775
AND NONE OF HER FRIENDS
SEEM TO KNOW EITHER.

00:00:41.808 --> 00:00:43.576 size:81% position:41%
OKAY, CONTACT THE CEDRIC'S
INTERNET PROVIDER

00:00:43.609 --> 00:00:45.311 size:78% position:39%
AND GET A LIST
OF ALL THE I.P. ADDRESSES

00:00:45.344 --> 00:00:47.647 size:75% position:38%
ACCESSED BY RESIDENTS
OVER THE PAST TWO WEEKS.

