UM, MOUNT HOPE CEMETERY
IN WESTCHESTER.

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.155 size:81% position:41%
SHE WAS KILLED LAST SUMMER
IN A CAR CRASH.

00:00:56.189 --> 00:00:57.891
WHAT WERE THE CIRCUMSTANCES?

00:00:57.924 --> 00:00:59.025
WELL, THERE WERE NO WITNESSES,

00:00:59.058 --> 00:01:00.326 align:start position:0%
BUT ACCORDING TO
THE POLICE REPORT,

00:01:00.360 --> 00:01:01.794
SHE WAS DRIVING HOME
FROM THE FIRM'S SUMMER PARTY.

00:01:01.828 --> 00:01:04.196 size:75% position:38%
SHE LOST CONTROL
AND CRASHED INTO A TREE.

00:01:04.229 --> 00:01:06.132
AUTOPSY INDICATES THAT SHE WAS
INTOXICATED AT THE TIME.

00:01:06.165 --> 00:01:08.901 size:75% position:38%
BUT ERIKA NEVER BELIEVED
THE OFFICIAL ACCOUNT.

00:01:08.935 --> 00:01:10.403
ANY REASON WHY?

00:01:10.437 --> 00:01:11.871 size:84% position:42%
WELL, SHE BELIEVED THAT PAM
WOULD NEVER DRIVE DRUNK.

00:01:11.904 --> 00:01:14.006 size:84% position:42%
AND WHEN THEY FOUND PAM,
SHE WAS WEARING HIGH HEELS,

00:01:14.039 --> 00:01:15.942 size:78% position:39%
AND ERIKA SAID
SHE NEVER DROVE IN HEELS.

00:01:15.975 --> 00:01:17.710 size:50% position:75%
THREE DEATHS,
ALL LEADING BACK

00:01:17.744 --> 00:01:20.380 size:59% position:70%
TO THE LAW FIRM
OF BANKS AND BAUER.

00:01:20.413 --> 00:01:21.681 size:84% position:58%
IS IT JUST ME, OR IS THIS

00:01:21.714 --> 00:01:24.017 align:end position:100%
STARTING TO SMELL LIKE
A JOHN GRISHAM NOVEL?

00:01:24.050 --> 00:01:26.085 size:66% position:67%
A SINGLE-CAR ACCIDENT
WITH NO WITNESSES?

00:01:26.118 --> 00:01:28.354
GUYS, THIS IS
A CLASSIC CONSPIRACY COVER-UP.

00:01:28.388 --> 00:01:30.423
THOUGH ONLY A LOWLY INTERN,

00:01:30.457 --> 00:01:32.959 size:84% position:58%
PAM STUMBLES ONTO SOMETHING
THE FIRM IS DOING,

00:01:33.026 --> 00:01:35.995 size:78% position:39%
SOMETHING BIG, NEFARIOUS.

00:01:36.029 --> 00:01:38.198 align:start position:0%
SHE HAS TO BE SILENCED,
ONLY AFTER THE ACCIDENT,

00:01:38.231 --> 00:01:39.565
BLAYLOCK CAN'T TAKE THE GUILT

00:01:39.598 --> 00:01:42.001 align:start position:0%
