WHATEVER IT IS,

00:01:55.348 --> 00:01:57.049
THE ONLY POSSIBLE EVIDENCE
IS ON ERIKA'S LAPTOP,

00:01:57.083 --> 00:01:58.351
WHICH OUR KILLER TOOK.

00:01:58.384 --> 00:01:59.619 align:start position:0%
